00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:49,360
[Story of Yanxi Palace]
[Episode 31]

3
00:01:50,820 --> 00:01:54,670
If doing this would
make everyone in the palace imitate it,

4
00:01:54,770 --> 00:01:56,630
then that is a truly good thing.

5
00:01:57,780 --> 00:01:59,850
When the Empress was in charge,

6
00:02:00,450 --> 00:02:02,820
she mainly focused on...

7
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,200
controlling the expenses.

8
00:02:05,470 --> 00:02:09,330
This induced a lot of criticisms
from some people in the palace.

9
00:02:09,650 --> 00:02:12,600
Now, you're the one in charge
of the palace affairs.

10
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:15,930
You are very meticulous and thorough.

11
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:18,950
You are respected by people in the palace.

12
00:02:19,850 --> 00:02:22,920
Just be bold and go with your plan.

13
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:26,160
With your trust, I will do my best.

14
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:28,070
One more thing,

15
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:30,980
as Zhili, Shandong and
other areas suffered from floods,

16
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:34,100
a lot of refugees are
migrating into the capital.

17
00:02:34,410 --> 00:02:36,860
porridge kitchens outside Di'an Gate.

18
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,930
One, it can provide disaster relief.

19
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:42,329
Second, it can serve as
praying for blessing for the Empress.

20
00:02:43,050 --> 00:02:46,960
It's a good thing to setup
porridge kitchens for disaster relief.

21
00:02:47,690 --> 00:02:50,650
But the food and money will be a problem.

22
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:55,110
We'll be using the money belonging to
the Imperial Household Department.

23
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:59,900
But life here in the palace
is already quite hard.

24
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:02,250
Every one is worried and looks bleak.

25
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,270
Isn't Consort Xian...

26
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:07,140
making it more difficult
for everyone by doing that?

27
00:03:07,140 --> 00:03:08,560
Noble Consort, don't worry.

28
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:12,180
Based on past experiences, we can
mobilise donations from gentry merchants.

29
00:03:12,180 --> 00:03:16,000
Please write
a decree about being benevolent.

30
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:19,410
People within the city would surely
rally together in response to it.

31
00:03:19,410 --> 00:03:22,770
By then, without touching
the Imperial Household Department vault,

32
00:03:22,770 --> 00:03:25,220
this problem can be resolved.

33
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:28,670
Consort Xian makes
thorough considerations.

34
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,270
This way,

35
00:03:30,350 --> 00:03:32,930
we can accumulate good karma
for the Empress...

36
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:36,100
and comfort the refugees.

37
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,940
It's hitting two birds with one stone.

38
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,920
Execute your plan boldly.

39
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,090
I will give you full support.

40
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,960
Thank you for you graces, Empress Dowager.

41
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:59,710
Consort Xian, you are highly
favoured by Empress Dowager.

42
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:02,440
You should be
well-contented with your success.

43
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:06,420
I'm doing my best to help
Empress Dowager and Empress.

44
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,940
I dare not bear what you've said.

45
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:12,890
Broaden the sources and
reduce the expenditures.

46
00:04:12,890 --> 00:04:15,790
Help with disaster relief and
set up porridge kitchens.

47
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:18,050
You are in a rush to win everyone's heart.

48
00:04:18,410 --> 00:04:20,700
Do you want to become the Empress?

49
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,320
Although Her Highness Empress may be sick,

50
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,970
Physician Ye is treating her,

51
00:04:24,970 --> 00:04:26,940
I believe she will recover soon.

52
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:29,210
I'm just managing
the matters in the palace.

53
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:30,950
I haven't done
anything that's beyond my duty.

54
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:32,440
My heart and affection...

55
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,130
can be proven by the heaven.

56
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:43,320
You performed well,

57
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:47,810
but I'm a professional performer.

58
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:51,450
I can't stand amateurs.

59
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,020
Zhi Lan, let's go.

60
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:06,840
She's jealous, so she made
slanderous remarks.

61
00:05:06,890 --> 00:05:08,910
Your Highness, what should we do?

62
00:05:10,030 --> 00:05:12,770
We will do what we should do.

63
00:05:13,510 --> 00:05:16,110
Noble Consort, your skin is like snow.

64
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,420
It's smooth and glistening.

65
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:19,630
I envy you a lot.

66
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:24,660
If you also moisturise yourself
with milk every day...

67
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:27,990
and soak in balsam,
you will be like this too.

68
00:05:28,090 --> 00:05:31,850
Noble Consort, you are a natural beauty
and the top beauty in the six palaces.

69
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:34,990
How would I dare to be compared to you?

70
00:05:35,090 --> 00:05:36,890
Stop being a glib talker.

71
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:41,550
I spent a lot of efforts and ideas...

72
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:45,100
before I was able to eliminate Empress
who was an eyesore.

73
00:05:45,250 --> 00:05:47,810
Who expected that Consort Xian...

74
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:51,890
would rescue Empress Dowager
at the Double Ninth Festival...

75
00:05:51,890 --> 00:05:54,050
and became famous overnight?

76
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,930
As for my strenuous fruits of labour,

77
00:05:59,290 --> 00:06:01,850
she has beaten me to it.

78
00:06:02,250 --> 00:06:03,740
Noble Consort,

79
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:07,320
Consort Xian has obtained
the favour of the Empress Dowager.

80
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:10,000
If you don't take actions now,

81
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:13,700
she will become political
and harder to go against in the future.

82
00:06:15,770 --> 00:06:19,900
She'll be at Di'an Gate
to help in the disaster relief.

83
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:23,080
Do you know what you should do?

84
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:28,020
Your Highness, don't worry. I understand.

85
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:30,550
We are distributing porridge
tomorrow outside Di'an Gate.

86
00:06:30,550 --> 00:06:32,310
Everyone must go and help out.

87
00:06:32,490 --> 00:06:33,720
Madam Liu,

88
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,990
we have piles of work on our hands.

89
00:06:36,090 --> 00:06:38,780
If we go to Di'an Gate tomorrow,
how will we finish our work?

90
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:40,510
Consort Xian has given the instructions.

91
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:43,300
Anyone from Labour House
that helps outside Di'an Gate...

92
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:46,270
will be rewarded with
one tael of silver and given a day off.

93
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:48,590
-That much?
-Consort Xian is really great.

94
00:06:48,590 --> 00:06:50,990
I have never received such rewards before.

95
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:56,070
That's right. Only Consort Xian
would remember slaves like us.

96
00:06:56,170 --> 00:06:59,370
-We are even given a day off.
-Enough, stop being long winded.

97
00:06:59,370 --> 00:07:00,560
Go back and rest now.

98
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:03,040
Be at Di'an Gate
tomorrow around midnight.

99
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,240
Yes.

100
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:10,050
Consort Xian said that...

101
00:07:10,150 --> 00:07:12,070
those in the six palaces who fall sick....

102
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,820
will be treated by a physician
and given a day off.

103
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:17,670
Consider yourself lucky.
Remain here tomorrow.

104
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:25,400
Everyone, dismiss.

105
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:38,620
Consort Xian has her own ways.

106
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:41,880
She calmly won everyone's heart.

107
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,430
Ying Luo,

108
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:45,750
compared to her, your Empress...

109
00:07:45,850 --> 00:07:47,990
lacks a lot.

110
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:50,700
Did I say anything wrong?

111
00:07:58,409 --> 00:08:01,370
Are you crazy? You have a fever.
What are you doing out here?

112
00:08:01,370 --> 00:08:02,380
Go back and rest.

113
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:06,530
What are you doing?

114
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:10,500
-Yuan Chun Wang, put me down.
-Stop talking. I'm your older brother.

115
00:08:11,710 --> 00:08:13,050
Put me down.

116
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:20,270
You are making preparations to keep vigil
at Consort Dowager Yu's tomb?

117
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,250
Yes.

118
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:24,500
How long will you be gone?

119
00:08:25,060 --> 00:08:26,100
Three years.

120
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:30,260
You are a very filial son.

121
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:37,090
I'm touched by your filial piety.

122
00:08:39,419 --> 00:08:41,620
I have always acted ridiculous,

123
00:08:42,309 --> 00:08:44,169
repeatedly created troubles...

124
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:46,370
and caused mother to worry,

125
00:08:46,830 --> 00:08:48,760
suffering from sleepless nights.

126
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:51,090
For all these years,

127
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,030
I have wronged her.

128
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:57,400
Being able to keep vigil
at her tomb for three years...

129
00:08:59,170 --> 00:09:00,560
is the only thing...

130
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,140
an unfilial son like me can do.

131
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,630
Unfilial son?

132
00:09:08,990 --> 00:09:10,010
Yes.

133
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,340
You are definitely a non-filial son.

134
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:19,280
You are the son of Consort Dowager Yu,

135
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,930
but you are also
the son of our late father!

136
00:09:21,930 --> 00:09:23,300
You are my brother,

137
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,270
a prince of the Great Qing!

138
00:09:27,220 --> 00:09:28,320
All these years,

139
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,370
you have been listening to a woman.

140
00:09:31,980 --> 00:09:34,520
Loitering around,
you have committed many wrongdoings.

141
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,750
You wasted a lot of time.

142
00:09:38,210 --> 00:09:40,670
As of now, you are still stubborn...

143
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,960
and doesn't know where your fault lies!

144
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,910
Why are you looking at me?

145
00:09:56,210 --> 00:09:57,720
Am I someone...

146
00:09:59,290 --> 00:10:02,010
who kill his siblings ruthlessly,

147
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:04,370
intolerant and not magnanimous?

148
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:12,740
Living in the palace,
Consort Dowager Yu...

149
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:15,360
had a pretty limited worldview.

150
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:17,910
She only knew that the event where...

151
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:20,590
the sons of the previous emperor competed
for the throne can't be repeated.

152
00:10:20,590 --> 00:10:23,260
But she almost killed you!

153
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,880
If it's as what she said,

154
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,080
you will always be a useless person.

155
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:30,930
You might as well hang yourself now...

156
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:33,920
lest you tarnish the reputation
of the Aisin Gioro clan!

157
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:34,930
Brother.

158
00:10:41,950 --> 00:10:42,950
Hong Zhou.

159
00:10:45,930 --> 00:10:47,830
I kept giving you chances.

160
00:10:47,930 --> 00:10:50,730
I have always hoped
you would open your heart to me.

161
00:10:52,290 --> 00:10:53,890
But I waited for ten years...

162
00:10:56,130 --> 00:10:58,240
and you are still so ridiculous.

163
00:10:58,590 --> 00:11:00,270
You are still so dim-witted.

164
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:06,840
Get lost.

165
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,100
Go and keep vigil at your mother's tomb.

166
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:11,160
Don't ever return to Forbidden City!

167
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:12,170
Brother!

168
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,160
I'm dim-witted.

169
00:11:14,370 --> 00:11:15,540
I was wrong.

170
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,520
Please forgive me.

171
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:24,130
Brother,

172
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,700
please forgive me.

173
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,340
Hong Zhou,

174
00:11:45,850 --> 00:11:48,310
you are a descendant
of the Aisin Gioro clan.

175
00:11:50,690 --> 00:11:53,260
The distinguished Prince He.

176
00:11:54,470 --> 00:11:56,400
If just to avoid political strife,

177
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:59,320
you would hide
your aspirations and dreams...

178
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:01,650
under the pretense of being ridiculous,

179
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:04,870
will you be able to face
our late father in the future?

180
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:07,940
Will you be able to face
the ancestors of the Great Qing?

181
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,230
I...

182
00:12:17,650 --> 00:12:19,000
will end my words here.

183
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:23,860
If you still have ambitions,

184
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,890
then consider carefully...

185
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,100
what you can do for...

186
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:33,310
our country...

187
00:12:37,210 --> 00:12:38,530
and our people.

188
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:51,190
Prince, you must be careful.

189
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:57,650
Well, what's wrong with him?

190
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:10,690
Stop!

191
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,600
Prince He.

192
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,880
Consort Xian.

193
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:28,940
you here to look for His Majesty?

194
00:13:29,050 --> 00:13:30,570
The palace is building porridge kitchens
to provide disaster relief.

195
00:13:30,570 --> 00:13:33,100
I need to present
some matters to His Majesty.

196
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:35,920
I'm busy.

197
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,580
I won't disturb you.

198
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,590
Prince He.

199
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:46,330
Consort Xian, do you still
have any instructions?

200
00:13:50,090 --> 00:13:52,550
Prince He, why are you crying?

201
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,250
I'm sorry.

202
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,940
I'm being disrespectful.

203
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:06,370
If you go out of the palace like this,

204
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,970
rumours will spread
all over the Forbidden City again,

205
00:14:08,970 --> 00:14:11,080
saying you and your brother
are on bad terms.

206
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:13,480
Thank you for reminding me, Your Highness.

207
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:16,340
My mother suddenly came to my mind.

208
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:19,260
The sudden burst of
sorrowful emotions...

209
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:20,990
probably made my eyes turn red.

210
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:23,480
You're a filial son. It's really touching.

211
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,950
But remorse and grief are useless.

212
00:14:26,050 --> 00:14:28,250
Why not do something more meaningful?

213
00:14:31,130 --> 00:14:32,680
We mentioned that...

214
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:35,820
Consort Xian will be distributing
porridge outside the Di'an Gate tomorrow.

215
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:38,230
This is a good matter
that will benefit the people.

216
00:14:38,230 --> 00:14:41,410
If you have the time to cry,
why don't you come and help out?

217
00:14:41,410 --> 00:14:43,920
You can accumulate
some good karma for Consort Dowager Yu.

218
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,580
Zhen, don't say nonsense.

219
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:47,910
But,

220
00:14:48,330 --> 00:14:49,950
if someone ridiculous like me...

221
00:14:49,950 --> 00:14:51,430
appears in Di'an Gate,

222
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:53,390
I fear that it will invite ridicule.

223
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,950
If you wants to do something serious...

224
00:14:54,950 --> 00:14:56,990
that will make others
look at you in a different way,

225
00:14:56,990 --> 00:14:59,950
the Di'an Gate
disaster relief is a good first step.

226
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,090
How did you know?

227
00:15:03,890 --> 00:15:07,120
Your thoughts are
all written on your face.

228
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:23,420
Prince!

229
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:25,570
I went to chat with some eunuchs.

230
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:27,110
When I returned, you were gone.

231
00:15:27,110 --> 00:15:28,760
Why didn't you call me?

232
00:15:31,450 --> 00:15:35,140
Are you serving me
or the other way around?

233
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:43,070
Is there anything on my face?

234
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:45,110
Prince, what am I looking for?

235
00:15:45,210 --> 00:15:47,010
Is there anything written on it?

236
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:50,350
No, there's nothing.

237
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:57,000
Not everyone is worthy of being described
as having a pure heart and spirit.

238
00:16:38,180 --> 00:16:40,120
Jin Xiu, where are you going?

239
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,530
I forgot something.
I'm going back to get it.

240
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:43,860
You all can leave first.

241
