Thank you.

251
00:17:24,500 --> 00:17:25,750
-Thank you.
-Fall in line properly!

252
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:27,170
Don't push forward!

253
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:29,960
Thank you.

254
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:31,520
Thank you.

255
00:17:31,620 --> 00:17:33,620
-Fall in line properly!
-Thank you.

256
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:39,710
Fall in line!

257
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:45,080
-Let us pass! We also want to eat!
-Don't push!

258
00:17:45,180 --> 00:17:47,150
Don't push! Go to the back of the line!

259
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:48,720
Don't push!
There are too many people in front!

260
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,650
Step back! First come first serve!

261
